{"data": {"node": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6859397944122034", "organization": {"id": "274498067660262", "viewer_permissions": [], "application_groupings": {"nodes": [{"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "6859397944122034"}]}, "id": "1181735076547542"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "5446476285387663"}]}, "id": "463985305463838"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "4317356281612249"}]}, "id": "3799404183428618"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "6859397944122034", "release_date": 1734026429, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9057155604346246"}, "id": "1132245561083197"}]}}, "binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6859397944122034", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9057155604346246"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "id": "8965059853555822", "version": "0.0.503", "version_code": 503, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1733240084, "id": "8965092303552577", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v20", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 18, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "8965093333552474"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "6859397944122034"}, "id": "8965093333552474", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": null, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "RELEASED", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "6859397944122034", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "582945257266604"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "3444095975720685", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "DigiGods", "keywords": [], "long_description": "..                                                                                                                                           \n                                                                                                                                                \n\n{1274137073702709}\n{8043697302400596}\n{481502264395865}\n{576810598270182}\n\n# CR\u00c9EZ, JOUEZ et PARTAGEZ dans un jeu bac \u00e0 sable bas\u00e9 sur la physique. Simulez tout type de jeu, du tir au parkour, avec le meilleur de la r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle. \n\n**Libert\u00e9 de Mouvement:** D\u00e9placez-vous en utilisant vos mains comme dans Gorilla Tag et No More Rainbows, ou avec le joystick, ou les deux !\n\n**Syst\u00e8me de Glisser-D\u00e9poser:** Intuitif et convivial, rendant le processus de cr\u00e9ation accessible \u00e0 tous.\n\n**Physique Multijoueur en Temps R\u00e9el:** Engagez-vous avec des amis et d'autres cr\u00e9ateurs dans un monde dynamique et pilot\u00e9 par la physique.\n\n**Possibilit\u00e9s Illimit\u00e9es:** Des jeux de tir d\u00e9fiant la gravit\u00e9 vers des puzzles complexes ! Cr\u00e9ez tout ce que vous imaginez et publiez vos cr\u00e9ations !\n\n**Action Instantan\u00e9e:** Plongez dans le jeu sans temps de chargement, gardant votre inspiration du moment.\n\n**Social et Interactif:** Partagez vos cr\u00e9ations avec une communaut\u00e9 de joueurs et de cr\u00e9ateurs, en participant au d\u00e9veloppement d'un environnement inspirant et sans limites.\"\n\n**Bac \u00e0 Sable RV/RM Innovant:** Un m\u00e9lange unique de r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle et de r\u00e9alit\u00e9 mixte qui offre une exp\u00e9rience de bac \u00e0 sable in\u00e9gal\u00e9e.", "short_description": "CR\u00c9EZ, JOUEZ et PARTAGEZ dans un jeu bac \u00e0 sable bas\u00e9 sur la physique. Simulez tout type de jeu, du tir au parkour, avec le meilleur de la r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle. \n\nNOUVEAU! Medieval Madness est arriv\u00e9! Voyagez dans le temps et vivez des combats \u00e0 l'\u00e9p\u00e9e \u00e9piques et un tir \u00e0 l'arc exaltant. Achevez vos ennemis en d\u00e9versant du feu du ciel depuis votre propre dragon!\n\nDigiGods est gratuit et le sera toujours."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Pixel_LineBreaks.png", "id": "1092435918988970", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974646_1092435922322303_935789645801789572_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jQYbfXFPR5cQ7kNvgE6iVeS&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAIHO6b1JRmsywgYqNaZClSnC9Gq0pkBPQQpH1OZ3i-1w&oe=67728A43"}, {"file_name": "Pixel_LineBreaks.png", "id": "597492492815404", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003251_597492496148737_1873900892775043926_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YcSS8a8ao-UQ7kNvgH4xsrY&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA82Zg6SZXDGC2iYlyYzyRitUJUzOEGKY98UScanr3Gcg&oe=677278DF"}, {"file_name": "DG Logo Immersive Layers.png", "id": "8912780688765225", "image_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_LOGO", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982711_8912780695431891_9132237625034303277_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=09Is9CMxbbYQ7kNvgEVNjPc&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB6Hkt-yo8dl1a5vYwGD2NqtqMq5qFV3LMBs1rB4gIwiw&oe=67729BC6"}, {"file_name": "Digigods_Multiverse_square.png", "id": "1704151243500305", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031396_1704151246833638_2069